io.spine.server.type

Interface MessageEnvelope<I extends com.google.protobuf.Message,T,C extends com.google.protobuf.Message>

  • Type Parameters:
    I - the type of the message ID
    T - the type of the object that wraps a message
    C - the type of the message context
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ActorMessageEnvelope<I,T,C>, EnrichableMessageEnvelope<I,T,M,C,E>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMessageEnvelope, CommandEnvelope, EventEnvelope, ExternalMessageEnvelope, ImportOrigin, RejectionEnvelope

    public interface MessageEnvelope<I extends com.google.protobuf.Message,T,C extends com.google.protobuf.Message>
    A common interface for obtaining messages from wrapping objects.
